{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "86bd0c20-a0c5-471c-8444-c021052cf9c7",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Doppelwarrior",
      "effect": "When a monster(s) is Special Summoned from your GY (except during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon this card from your hand. If this card is sent to the GY as Synchro Material: You can Special Summon 2 \"Doppel Tokens\" (Warrior/DARK/Level 1/ATK 400/DEF 400) in Attack Position."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Guerrier Double",
      "effect": "Lorsqu'un ou plusieurs monstres sont Invoqu\u00e9s Sp\u00e9cialement depuis votre Cimeti\u00e8re (sauf durant la Damage Step) : vous pouvez Invoquer Sp\u00e9cialement cette carte depuis votre main. Si cette carte est envoy\u00e9e au Cimeti\u00e8re comme Mat\u00e9riel Synchro : vous pouvez Invoquer Sp\u00e9cialement 2 \"Jeton Double\" (Guerrier/T\u00c9N\u00c8BRES/Niveau 1/ATK 400/DEF 400) en Position d'Attaque."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Doppelkrieger",
      "effect": "Wenn ein oder mehr Monster als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung von deinem Friedhof beschworen werden (au\u00dfer w\u00e4hrend des Damage Steps): Du kannst diese Karte als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung von deiner Hand beschw\u00f6ren. Falls diese Karte als Synchromaterial auf den Friedhof gelegt wird: Du kannst 2 \u201eDoppel-Spielmarken\u201c (Krieger/FINSTERNIS/Stufe 1/ATK 400/DEF 400) als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung in die Angriffsposition beschw\u00f6ren."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Doppioguerriero",
      "effect": "Quando uno o pi\u00f9 mostri vengono Evocati Specialmente dal tuo Cimitero (eccetto durante il Damage Step): puoi Evocare Specialmente questa carta dalla tua mano. Se questa carta viene mandata al Cimitero come Materiale Synchro: puoi Evocare Specialmente 2 \"Segna-Doppio\" (Guerriero/OSCURIT\u00c0/Livello 1/ATK 400/DEF 400) in Posizione di Attacco."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Guerreiro Doppel",
      "effect": "Quando um ou mais monstros forem Invocados por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Especial do seu Cemit\u00e9rio (exceto durante a Etapa de Dano): voc\u00ea pode Invocar este card por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Especial da sua m\u00e3o. Se este card for enviado para o Cemit\u00e9rio como Mat\u00e9ria Sincro: voc\u00ea pode Invocar por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Especial 2 \"Ficha de Doppel\" (Guerreiro/TREVAS/N\u00edvel 1/ATK 400/DEF 400) em Posi\u00e7\u00e3o de Ataque."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Guerrero Doble",
      "effect": "Cuando uno o m\u00e1s monstruos son Invocados de Modo Especial desde tu Cementerio (excepto durante el Damage Step): puedes Invocar esta carta de Modo Especial desde tu mano. Si esta carta es mandada al Cementerio como Material de Sincron\u00eda: puedes Invocar de Modo Especial 2 \"Ficha Doble\" (Guerrero/OSCURIDAD/Nivel 1/ATK 400/DEF 400) en Posici\u00f3n de Ataque."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u30c9\u30c3\u30da\u30eb\u30fb\u30a6\u30a9\u30ea\u30a2\u30fc",
      "effect": "\u2460\uff1a\u81ea\u5206\u306e\u5893\u5730\u304b\u3089\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u304c\u7279\u6b8a\u53ec\u559a\u3055\u308c\u305f\u6642\u306b\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u3092\u624b\u672d\u304b\u3089\u7279\u6b8a\u53ec\u559a\u3059\u308b\u3002\u2461\uff1a\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\uff33\u7d20\u6750\u3068\u3057\u3066\u5893\u5730\u3078\u9001\u3089\u308c\u305f\u5834\u5408\u306b\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u81ea\u5206\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u306b\u300c\u30c9\u30c3\u30da\u30eb\u30fb\u30c8\u30fc\u30af\u30f3\u300d\uff08\u6226\u58eb\u65cf\u30fb\u95c7\u30fb\u661f\uff11\u30fb\u653b\uff0f\u5b88\uff14\uff10\uff10\uff09\uff12\u4f53\u3092\u653b\u6483\u8868\u793a\u3067\u7279\u6b8a\u53ec\u559a\u3059\u308b\u3002"
    },
    "ko": {
      "name": "\ub3c4\ud50c \uc6cc\ub9ac\uc5b4",
      "effect": "\u2460: \uc790\uc2e0 \ubb18\uc9c0\uc5d0\uc11c \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\uac00 \ud2b9\uc218 \uc18c\ud658\ub418\uc5c8\uc744 \ub54c\uc5d0 \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\ub97c \ud328\uc5d0\uc11c \ud2b9\uc218 \uc18c\ud658\ud55c\ub2e4. \u2461: \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\uac00 \uc2f1\ud06c\ub85c \uc18c\uc7ac\ub85c\uc11c \ubb18\uc9c0\ub85c \ubcf4\ub0b4\uc84c\uc744 \uacbd\uc6b0\uc5d0 \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \uc790\uc2e0 \ud544\ub4dc\uc5d0 \"\ub3c4\ud50c \ud1a0\ud070\"(\uc804\uc0ac\uc871 / \uc5b4\ub460 / \ub808\ubca8 1 / \uacf5 400 / \uc218 400) 2\uc7a5\uc744 \uacf5\uaca9 \ud45c\uc2dc\ub85c \ud2b9\uc218 \uc18c\ud658\ud55c\ub2e4."
    },
